---
import LogoLight from "../assets/MadNess Music Group - Logo White.png";
import LogoDark from "../assets/MadNess Music Group - Logo Black.png";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<section id="hero" class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-12 items-center">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 md:col-start-3">
        <div class="hero-logo-wrap">
          <img
            src={LogoDark.src}
            alt="Madness Music Group"
            class="hero-logo hero-logo-light"
          />

          <img
            src={LogoLight.src}
            alt="Madness Music Group"
            class="hero-logo hero-logo-dark"
          />
        </div>

<span
  class="absolute right-0.5 top-2/6 -translate-y-1/2 text-[25vw] font-anton opacity-[0.03] select-none text-white/20"
  aria-hidden="true"
>
  MADNESS
</span>

        <div class="pt-20 sm:pt-28 md:pt-32">
<span class="block text-2xl tracking-wider uppercase opacity-70 mb-8">
  <span class="text-[#ed7651]">Sello Independiente</span> · Distribución · Plataforma Musical
</span>

<div class="w-35 h-0.5 bg-[#ed7651]/80 mb-6"></div>

          <p class="text-sm md:text-base opacity-80 leading-relaxed max-w-120 mb-15">
  Lanzamos, distribuímos y apoyamos artistas emergentes mientras construímos un ecosistema curado para la música contemporánea.
</p>

        <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap">
<a
  href="/submit"
  class="
  inline-flex items-center justify-center
  px-9 py-4
  rounded-full
  text-[11px]
  tracking-[0.45em]
  uppercase
  bg-[#ed7651]
  text-white
  transition-all duration-300 ease-out
  hover:scale-[1.02]
  active:scale-[0.98]
  hover:shadow-[0_12px_40px_rgba(237,118,81,0.35)]
"
>
  Enviar música
</a>
<a
  href="#playlists"
  class="
  inline-flex items-center justify-center
  px-9 py-4
  rounded-full
  text-[11px]
  tracking-[0.45em]
  uppercase
  border border-base-content/30
  text-base-content/70
  transition-all duration-300 ease-out
  hover:border-[#ed7651]
  hover:text-[#ed7651]
  hover:-translate-y-0.5
"
>
  Explorar
</a>



</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
